cu.explanation_en: Setting the transport preference to an unknown value 'invalid' will cause F1 interface initialization failures and prevent proper CU-DU communication.

du.explanation_en: Setting the ASN.1 verbosity to an unknown value 'invalid' will cause the ASN.1 processing to fail and potentially crash the DU during message encoding/decoding.
du.explanation_zh: 將 ASN.1 詳細程度設定為未知值 'invalid' 會導致 ASN.1 處理失敗，並可能在訊息編碼/解碼期間崩潰 DU。
